OL,3,CPolice appeal for witnesses after
OL,4,Cairsoft gun found at scene of fight
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for witnesses
OL,7,Fafter officers found an airsoft gun at
OL,8,Fthe scene of a fight in Newport.
OL,10,FGwent Police said, "At around 6:15 pm
OL,11,Fon Saturday 11 April, we received a
OL,12,Freport that a group of men had been
OL,13,Ffighting in Oliphant Circle, Newport.
OL,15,F"Officers attended and conducted a
OL,16,Fsearch of the area. While no persons
OL,17,Fwere located or any reports of injury
OL,18,Fmade, an airsoft gun was recovered and
OL,19,Fseized nearby.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
