OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776258665
OL,3,CPolice appeal for witnesses after
OL,4,Cairsoft gun found at scene of fight
OL,6,F"It is also believed that three cars
OL,7,Fwere involved; all three cars have
OL,8,Fsince been located and recovered."
OL,10,FThe force added that the incident is
OL,11,Fnot thought to be linked to an alleged
OL,12,Fassault on Friday, 10th April, in
OL,13,Fwhich three teenagers were injured
OL,14,Fafter allegedly being shot at by a man
OL,15,Fcarrying an air gun.
OL,17,FDCI Matthew Edwards, the senior
OL,18,Finvestigating officer, said, "We
OL,19,Funderstand that reports of this nature
OL,20,Fare deeply concerning for our
OL,21,Fcommunities."
